trans-unit.source: Represents the name of a queue associated with an event on a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance"></xref>.
This class cannot be inherited.

> [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class can be associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> or any other queues used by the Workflow Foundation (WF).
